## 3. Viewpoints

This SDD uses the seven viewpoints defined by IEEE 1016-2009:

| Viewpoint      | Purpose                                                    |
|----------------|------------------------------------------------------------|
| Composition    | System decomposition into subsystems and components        |
| Logical        | Domain concepts, business rules, functional behavior       |
| Dependency     | Import/use/call relationships between components           |
| Interface      | Public APIs, data contracts, integration points            |
| Information    | Persistent data models, state machines                     |
| Interaction    | Sequence and collaboration diagrams for key scenarios      |
| Implementation | Technology stack, directory layout, deployment topology    |

