### 4.6 Interaction View

#### 4.6.1 [Use Case — e.g., User submits a request]

*Covers*: REQ-{{REQ_ID_PREFIX}}-001

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as API Layer
    participant DB as Database

    User->>FE: Submit form
